PN,40901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773069078
OL,3,CVan driver who drove into and killed
OL,4,Cuniversity student jailed
OL,6,FA former van driver has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor eight years after he drove into
OL,8,Fand killed a university student and
OL,9,Fseriously injured two others.
OL,11,FChristopher Jackson was sentenced
OL,12,Ftoday after he killed 20-year-old
OL,13,FAalia Mahomed in a fatal collision
OL,14,FAldwych last March.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Superintendent Donna
OL,17,FSmith, from the Metropolitan Police ,
OL,18,Fsaid:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773069078
OL,3,CVan driver who drove into and killed
OL,4,Cuniversity student jailed
OL,6,F"It is almost a year to the day since
OL,7,Fthis terrible incident took place. It
OL,8,Fshould never have happened, and Aalia
OL,9,Fshould still be with us today,
OL,10,Fsurrounded by those who loved her.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts, as always, remain with
OL,13,FAalia's family and friends. Their
OL,14,Fstrength over the past year has been
OL,15,Fextraordinary. We cannot begin to
OL,16,Fimagine the immeasurable suffering
OL,17,Fthey have been through since last
OL,18,FMarch.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773069078
OL,3,CVan driver who drove into and killed
OL,4,Cuniversity student jailed
OL,6,F"We would also like to share our
OL,7,Fthoughts with the two other victims,
OL,8,Fwhose lives have been forever changed.
OL,9,FThey continue to show remarkable
OL,10,Fcourage, and we know their lives will
OL,11,Fnever be the same.
OL,13,F"Finally, I'd like to thank everyone
OL,14,Finvolved in this investigation. We
OL,15,Fhope that this case serves as a
OL,16,Freminder of the consequences of
OL,17,Fdangerous driving."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773069078
OL,3,CVan driver who drove into and killed
OL,4,Cuniversity student jailed
OL,6,FOn the morning of the incident,
OL,7,FJackson arrived at work and was
OL,8,Fassigned, alongside a colleague, to
OL,9,Fcollect two electric vehicles from
OL,10,FBush House in Aldwych.
OL,12,FAfter leaving Bush House's courtyard,
OL,13,FJackson drove at speed towards a set
OL,14,Fof iron gates leading to the
OL,15,Fpedestrian zone of The Strand.
OL,17,FJackson collided with the gates, which
OL,18,Ffell and hit a woman and man in their
OL,19,Ftwenties. They were both taken to
OL,20,Fhospital having sustained 'life
OL,21,Fchanging' injuries.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773069078
OL,3,CVan driver who drove into and killed
OL,4,Cuniversity student jailed
OL,6,FJackson continued driving, and the van
OL,7,Fbriefly flew into the air before
OL,8,Fcolliding with Aalia who was sitting
OL,9,Fon a bench on the other side of the
OL,10,Fflower bed.
OL,12,FAalia was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,14,FRoy Pershad, for the Crown Prosecution
OL,15,FService, said:
OL,17,F"Our thoughts remain with all those
OL,18,Fwho knew and loved Aalia Mahomed, as
OL,19,Fwell as with the other victims who
OL,20,Fwere seriously injured.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773069078
OL,3,CVan driver who drove into and killed
OL,4,Cuniversity student jailed
OL,6,F"This must be an unimaginably
OL,7,Fdifficult time for all concerned.
OL,9,F"This was a catastrophic crash which
OL,10,Fclaimed the life of Aalia, a young
OL,11,Fwoman with her whole future ahead of
OL,12,Fher, and left two other people with
OL,13,Flife-changing injuries.
OL,15,F"Every person who gets behind the
OL,16,Fwheel has a responsibility to drive
OL,17,Fsafely and with due care for those
OL,18,Faround them ` the consequences when
OL,19,Fthat driving falls short of that
OL,20,Fresponsibility can be devastating.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773069078
OL,3,CVan driver who drove into and killed
OL,4,Cuniversity student jailed
OL,6,F"The Crown Prosecution Service
OL,7,Fcarefully reviewed the evidence and
OL,8,Fworked closely with our police
OL,9,Fcolleagues to build the strongest
OL,10,Fpossible case. Jackson subsequently
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to all charges brought
OL,12,Fagainst him.
OL,14,F"We hope today's sentence provides
OL,15,Fsome measure of justice and comfort to
OL,16,FAalia's family and to the other
OL,17,Fvictims, as they continue to grieve
OL,18,Fand recover."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773069078
OL,3,CVan driver who drove into and killed
OL,4,Cuniversity student jailed
OL,6,FThe young woman was studying physics
OL,7,Fand philosophy. Her family described
OL,8,Fher as "a bright, kind and beautiful
OL,9,Fsoul, who brought joy and laughter to
OL,10,Feveryone around her."
OL,12,FHundreds of witnesses came forward
OL,13,Fafter the event. Jackson had been kept
OL,14,Fin custody until his sentencing today.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/8
